OL,6,FChildren as young as seven are
OL,7,Fpotentially being sent violent and
OL,8,Fexplicit messages on the popular
OL,9,Fsocial media site Snapchat, Police has
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FIt is believed that more than 50 local
OL,13,Fchildren are thought to be part of a
OL,14,Fgroup where "harmful content" such as
OL,15,Fstrong sexual language and images are
OL,16,Fbeing shared.
OL,18,FSome of the messages seen by ITV News
OL,19,Finclude, "send me pics of your t*ts"
OL,20,Fand "I'll make you so miserable you
OL,21,Fwon't want to be here".
