OL,6,FGuernsey Police officer Laura Simpson
OL,7,Fspecialises in digital safety and is
OL,8,Fcurrently running an education
OL,9,Fprogramme in schools that includes
OL,10,Fwarnings about harmful sexual
OL,11,Fbehaviours.
OL,13,FShe said: "Snapchat is not suitable
OL,14,Ffor children at all. The age
OL,15,Frestriction of 13+ clearly isn't
OL,16,Fdeterring families from allowing their
OL,17,Fchildren into this environment, and
OL,18,Fthat is putting children at serious
OL,19,Frisk of sexual exploitation."
