OL,6,FA spokesperson for Snapchat said:
OL,7,F"Snapchat is for over 13s and we are
OL,8,Fcommitted to ensuring our app is both
OL,9,Fsafe and age-appropriate.
OL,11,F"If we find sexual or harmful content
OL,12,Fwe remove it immediately and we work
OL,13,Fwith police to support investigations.
OL,15,F"We also have extra protections in
OL,16,Fplace for younger users, confidential
OL,17,Fin-app reporting tools so our
OL,18,Fcommunity can tell us if they see
OL,19,Finappropriate content and our Family
OL,20,FCentre, which allows parents to see
OL,21,Fwho their teens are talking to."
